{"tid":1763761,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"史維：年青人所為是沒第二條路下才做的反應","createTime":"2019-11-30T15:05:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-30T15:11:11.000Z","uid":125168,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"19a5ba6a74fc82a0bf3de61f7a63c1efa78dd777","tid":1763761,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T15:05:56.000Z","msg":"史維：年青人所為是沒第二條路下才做的反應<br />\n <br />\n【Now新聞台】史維科大校長史維指，過去數月有人對政治訴求有較多想法，亦有人認為不應為訴求犧牲生活上的舒適，雙方並非完全互相衝突。<br />\n<br />\n史維：「對目前情況不滿意，包括年青人、學生在內，他們絕大多數人並不想犧牲自己然後不顧一切，他們做的事，我覺得是沒有第二條路的情況下才做的一個反應，我覺得我們必須了解，也必須給他們一個安慰。」"},{"pid":"ffa8e4b1db47ef45cc9298330fec2b2d4cca1743","tid":1763761,"uid":125168,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T15:07:11.000Z","msg":"btw 唔好再將場運動spin去後生到，後生仔可能係主力，但7成人都支持五大訴求<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65f8ccac2f76672a02e31db914448e941cea04c1","tid":1763761,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T15:08:04.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"e1d6810bf779865aff44601484699667a4b9bdb5","tid":1763761,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T15:08:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9109f601cec61da600d74e80e1ccdf498cf665e","tid":1763761,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T15:09:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"feb00aa5335f3b6e88a2935330916a5bbf1c4cdb","tid":1763761,"uid":21545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T15:09:43.000Z","msg":"勿吹奏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我相信佢怕<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 多於真心"},{"pid":"9b4d0330e428a7c0575d4469225bf887e3d57f8b","tid":1763761,"uid":108337